[
    {
        "index": 1,
        "start_time": 6856,
        "end_time": 12167,
        "text": "Some of the world&#39;s most recognizable\nsymbols exist to sell products,"
    },
    {
        "index": 2,
        "start_time": 12167,
        "end_time": 14316,
        "text": "others to steer traffic"
    },
    {
        "index": 3,
        "start_time": 14316,
        "end_time": 16887,
        "text": "or advance political causes."
    },
    {
        "index": 4,
        "start_time": 16887,
        "end_time": 20766,
        "text": "But there&#39;s one whose main purpose\nis to help people."
    },
    {
        "index": 5,
        "start_time": 20766,
        "end_time": 26616,
        "text": "You may know it as the wheelchair symbol,\nor a sign for people with disabilities,"
    },
    {
        "index": 6,
        "start_time": 26616,
        "end_time": 30397,
        "text": "but its formal title as maintained\nby the ISO"
    },
    {
        "index": 7,
        "start_time": 30397,
        "end_time": 33875,
        "text": "is the International Symbol of Access."
    },
    {
        "index": 8,
        "start_time": 33875,
        "end_time": 35494,
        "text": "But despite its familiarity,"
    },
    {
        "index": 9,
        "start_time": 35494,
        "end_time": 39387,
        "text": "many people are unclear as to what \nthe symbol actually means,"
    },
    {
        "index": 10,
        "start_time": 39387,
        "end_time": 44246,
        "text": "which has a lot to do with the symbol\nitself and the way it came about."
    },
    {
        "index": 11,
        "start_time": 44246,
        "end_time": 49038,
        "text": "In 1968, the International Commission\non Technology and Accessibility"
    },
    {
        "index": 12,
        "start_time": 49038,
        "end_time": 50967,
        "text": "held a design contest."
    },
    {
        "index": 13,
        "start_time": 50967,
        "end_time": 52448,
        "text": "They were looking for a symbol"
    },
    {
        "index": 14,
        "start_time": 52448,
        "end_time": 55617,
        "text": "that would be readily identifiable \nfrom a reasonable distance,"
    },
    {
        "index": 15,
        "start_time": 55617,
        "end_time": 57108,
        "text": "self-descriptive,"
    },
    {
        "index": 16,
        "start_time": 57108,
        "end_time": 58043,
        "text": "simple,"
    },
    {
        "index": 17,
        "start_time": 58043,
        "end_time": 58928,
        "text": "practical,"
    },
    {
        "index": 18,
        "start_time": 58928,
        "end_time": 61939,
        "text": "and couldn&#39;t be confused\nwith existing signage."
    },
    {
        "index": 19,
        "start_time": 61939,
        "end_time": 64320,
        "text": "The winning design, \nwhich didn&#39;t have a head,"
    },
    {
        "index": 20,
        "start_time": 64320,
        "end_time": 68557,
        "text": "was created by a Danish designer\nnamed Susanne Koefed."
    },
    {
        "index": 21,
        "start_time": 68557,
        "end_time": 72328,
        "text": "The addition of a head a year later\ngave it a more human form,"
    },
    {
        "index": 22,
        "start_time": 72328,
        "end_time": 73677,
        "text": "and within ten years,"
    },
    {
        "index": 23,
        "start_time": 73677,
        "end_time": 77699,
        "text": "it was endorsed by both the United Nations\nand the ISO."
    },
    {
        "index": 24,
        "start_time": 77699,
        "end_time": 82426,
        "text": "With minimal cost and minimal fuss,\na global icon was born."
    },
    {
        "index": 25,
        "start_time": 82426,
        "end_time": 85058,
        "text": "There have been a few tweaks\nover the decades."
    },
    {
        "index": 26,
        "start_time": 85058,
        "end_time": 89038,
        "text": "The Graphic Artists Guild added more\nrounded, human-like features,"
    },
    {
        "index": 27,
        "start_time": 89038,
        "end_time": 95189,
        "text": "and in 2012, the Accessible Icon Project\nproduced a more dynamic version."
    },
    {
        "index": 28,
        "start_time": 95189,
        "end_time": 97600,
        "text": "But what does it really represent?"
    },
    {
        "index": 29,
        "start_time": 97600,
        "end_time": 98889,
        "text": "What&#39;s its purpose?"
    },
    {
        "index": 30,
        "start_time": 98889,
        "end_time": 104178,
        "text": "Put simply, it&#39;s a sign to identify where\nthere are accessible facilities."
    },
    {
        "index": 31,
        "start_time": 104178,
        "end_time": 106911,
        "text": "The strength of such an internationally\nrecognized image"
    },
    {
        "index": 32,
        "start_time": 106911,
        "end_time": 108560,
        "text": "is that wherever you travel,"
    },
    {
        "index": 33,
        "start_time": 108560,
        "end_time": 112781,
        "text": "you don&#39;t need to speak the language\nor have in-depth cultural knowledge."
    },
    {
        "index": 34,
        "start_time": 112781,
        "end_time": 116889,
        "text": "If you require an accessible toilet,\nthe sign shows the way."
    },
    {
        "index": 35,
        "start_time": 116889,
        "end_time": 120030,
        "text": "But the confusion comes \nfrom the term accessibility"
    },
    {
        "index": 36,
        "start_time": 120030,
        "end_time": 122141,
        "text": "and what that actually means."
    },
    {
        "index": 37,
        "start_time": 122141,
        "end_time": 125402,
        "text": "Many people assume that because\nthe symbol depicts a wheelchair,"
    },
    {
        "index": 38,
        "start_time": 125402,
        "end_time": 130321,
        "text": "that accessible facilities are meant\nonly for people who use wheelchairs,"
    },
    {
        "index": 39,
        "start_time": 130321,
        "end_time": 134221,
        "text": "or those, at the very least,\nwho have a visible physical condition."
    },
    {
        "index": 40,
        "start_time": 134221,
        "end_time": 136761,
        "text": "But accessibility is a broad concept"
    },
    {
        "index": 41,
        "start_time": 136761,
        "end_time": 139471,
        "text": "that applies to many, \nmany different conditions."
    },
    {
        "index": 42,
        "start_time": 139471,
        "end_time": 141219,
        "text": "That includes people with autism,"
    },
    {
        "index": 43,
        "start_time": 141219,
        "end_time": 142592,
        "text": "visual impairments,"
    },
    {
        "index": 44,
        "start_time": 142592,
        "end_time": 144232,
        "text": "and autoimmune diseases,"
    },
    {
        "index": 45,
        "start_time": 144232,
        "end_time": 147032,
        "text": "like lupus, which can cause \npain and fatigue,"
    },
    {
        "index": 46,
        "start_time": 147032,
        "end_time": 149332,
        "text": "along with many other conditions."
    },
    {
        "index": 47,
        "start_time": 149332,
        "end_time": 152012,
        "text": "In fact, the World Health \nOrganization estimates"
    },
    {
        "index": 48,
        "start_time": 152012,
        "end_time": 154631,
        "text": "that there are approximately\n1 billion people"
    },
    {
        "index": 49,
        "start_time": 154631,
        "end_time": 157632,
        "text": "who experience some form of disability,"
    },
    {
        "index": 50,
        "start_time": 157632,
        "end_time": 160943,
        "text": "which means that this group is very\nlikely to include yourself,"
    },
    {
        "index": 51,
        "start_time": 160943,
        "end_time": 162230,
        "text": "or a family member,"
    },
    {
        "index": 52,
        "start_time": 162230,
        "end_time": 163192,
        "text": "a classmate,"
    },
    {
        "index": 53,
        "start_time": 163192,
        "end_time": 164204,
        "text": "a friend,"
    },
    {
        "index": 54,
        "start_time": 164204,
        "end_time": 165712,
        "text": "or a work colleague."
    },
    {
        "index": 55,
        "start_time": 165712,
        "end_time": 169583,
        "text": "And people who use wheelchairs only\nmake up about 65 million,"
    },
    {
        "index": 56,
        "start_time": 169583,
        "end_time": 172623,
        "text": "or 15% of the total."
    },
    {
        "index": 57,
        "start_time": 172623,
        "end_time": 176323,
        "text": "The vast majority \nhave non-visible disabilities."
    },
    {
        "index": 58,
        "start_time": 176323,
        "end_time": 179693,
        "text": "Accessible parking spaces, facilities,\nand entrances"
    },
    {
        "index": 59,
        "start_time": 179693,
        "end_time": 183552,
        "text": "are designed with \nthat entire group in mind."
    },
    {
        "index": 60,
        "start_time": 183552,
        "end_time": 188183,
        "text": "So it&#39;s easy to see why in recent years\npeople have begun to raise questions"
    },
    {
        "index": 61,
        "start_time": 188183,
        "end_time": 192434,
        "text": "about whether the symbol is really\nappropriate for what it&#39;s meant to do."
    },
    {
        "index": 62,
        "start_time": 192434,
        "end_time": 194484,
        "text": "And it&#39;s not just about accuracy."
    },
    {
        "index": 63,
        "start_time": 194484,
        "end_time": 196686,
        "text": "It&#39;s common for people \nto become indignant,"
    },
    {
        "index": 64,
        "start_time": 196686,
        "end_time": 198207,
        "text": "sometimes abusive,"
    },
    {
        "index": 65,
        "start_time": 198207,
        "end_time": 203337,
        "text": "when they see people without visible\ndisabilities using accessible facilities."
    },
    {
        "index": 66,
        "start_time": 203337,
        "end_time": 206167,
        "text": "The symbol is unfortunately creating\nwidespread issues"
    },
    {
        "index": 67,
        "start_time": 206167,
        "end_time": 210387,
        "text": "for the very people and families\nit&#39;s meant to help."
    },
    {
        "index": 68,
        "start_time": 210387,
        "end_time": 213226,
        "text": "The recent redesigns have attempted\nwith some success"
    },
    {
        "index": 69,
        "start_time": 213226,
        "end_time": 216268,
        "text": "to acknowledge concerns \nover the current symbol."
    },
    {
        "index": 70,
        "start_time": 216268,
        "end_time": 219878,
        "text": "But some think that a complete redesign\nis in order."
    },
    {
        "index": 71,
        "start_time": 219878,
        "end_time": 221507,
        "text": "It&#39;s a difficult task, though."
    },
    {
        "index": 72,
        "start_time": 221507,
        "end_time": 226507,
        "text": "How do you replace a symbol \nthat&#39;s familiar the world over?"
    },
    {
        "index": 73,
        "start_time": 226507,
        "end_time": 228587,
        "text": "And what do you replace it with?"
    }
]